# ── Epic schema ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Epics use a smaller, parallel contract to tasks. Status vocabulary is
# constrained so `pm epic list --status in-progress`-style filtering works the
# same way it does for tasks. Aliases mirror the task drift seen in the wild
# (epics historically used the bare `updated`/`completed`/`started` keys).
